2052.subject: ESSP
2052.descrlong: Students in this service learning course will focus on fundamental issues about inclusive science curriculum design and pedagogy for multicultural populations. Requires successful completion of coursework that satisfies the SCIENCE ULR. (Not offered in 2003-2004.)
